      <text fn="Arial" fh="15" fc="16777215" fa="1" charset="238">Astatine is a radioactive element. It is a solid, soluble in organic solvents. Similar to other fluorine group elements, it is a non-metal, although it exhibits certain metallic properties. All its isotopes have very short half-lives; the most stable one </text>
   </par>
